message.body: Hey how's it going ? What time the party get done?
I think three.. but honestly after you left I went to sleep on the couch while the party was still going on lol
Haha all that work knocked you out
Did you just sleep downstairs all night?

Yea... between the baby all week giving me 3 hours of sleep each night, working, baking a cake, and fitness training I was so beat then had to run around for the party and decorate. And taking the physical exam yesterday made me so sore! Im feeling it today!
Is the house still a mess?
Carlos is playing with my phone
Huh? And no its not. We are almost finished. Victor cane over to help. He and I banged it out
